data.name: Liepard
data.flavorText: Don't be fooled by its gorgeous fur and elegant figure. This is a moody and vicious Pokémon.

data.name: Liepard

attacks.name: Torment
attacks.text: Choose 1 of your opponent's Active Pokémon's attacks. That Pokémon can't use that attack during your opponent's next turn.

data.flavorText: Their beautiful form comes from the muscles they have developed. They run silently in the night.

data.name: Liepard

attacks.name: Gentle Bite
attacks.text: During your opponent's next turn, any damage done by attacks from the Defending Pokémon is reduced by 60 (before applying Weakness and Resistance).

attacks.name: Mach Claw
attacks.text: This attack's damage isn't affected by Resistance.

data.flavorText: Their beautiful form comes from the muscles they have developed. They run silently in the night.

data.name: Liepard

attacks.name: Taunt
attacks.text: Switch the Defending Pokémon with 1 of your opponent's Benched Pokémon.

attacks.name: Sucker Punch
attacks.text: If this Pokémon has any Darkness Energy attached to it, this attack does 30 more damage.

data.flavorText: Stealthily, it sneaks up on its target, striking from behind before its victim has a chance to react.

data.name: Liepard

attacks.name: Feint Attack
attacks.text: Does 30 damage to 1 of your opponent's Pokémon. This attack's damage isn't affected by Weakness, Resistance, or any other effects on that Pokémon.

attacks.name: Claw Rend
attacks.text: If the Defending Pokémon already has any damage counters on it, this attack does 30 more damage.

data.flavorText: These Pokémon vanish and appear unexpectedly. Many Trainers are drawn to their beautiful form and fur.
